I can't believe i got 5th place, so many months of grinding and fails in 8-4 and all the missed BBG's and frustrations it finally happened. this is the single greatest accomplishment i've achieved in speedrunning. With this run i bopped i_o_l and became the best player in any% on emulator, which is a feat i never thought i could reach.
